data.description: WATERFRONT!!! Nestled in a quiet community you'll find your long-awaited treasure!!!  3 sizeable bedrooms and 2 full bathrooms with a full basement awaiting your vision.  The kitchen, dining, and living areas boast an open concept for entertaining or just relaxing and enjoying peaceful moments.  On nearly 1/2 acre, you find sufficient yard space for your outdoor activities and enjoyment.  The front yards also boast a serene garden for quiet reflection as well.   If you are looking for a home, stop the search, you have found it with this lovely craftsman-style rambler.  Did we forget to mention the spacious front porch and rear deck and the short walk to Lake Lariat?  You don't want to miss this!  Schedule your visit today.
